title: Paradise Valley Market, Inc. (Carnival Supermarket) Recalls Ground Beef Productsdue To Possible E. Coli O157:H7 Adulteration
summary: WASHINGTON, Sept. 8, 2016 The Paradise Valley Market, Inc. (Carnival Supermarket), located at 870 3rd Avenue, Chula Vista, Calif., is voluntarily recalling approximately 35 pounds of ground beef products that may be adulterated with E. coli O157:H7, the U.S. Department of Agricultures Food Safety and...
